1-Componentes que son acciones, mediante uri: "action=TestRequestResponse&greeting=Hello"

2-Datos:
Estructura de datos JSON:
{"data":[
    {"firstName":"John", "lastName":"Doe"},
    {"firstName":"Anna", "lastName":"Smith"},
    {"firstName":"Peter", "lastName":"Jones"}
]}

{"data":[
    {"last_name": "Doe", "first_name": "John"}, 
    {"last_name": "Smith", "first_name": "Ana"}, 
    {"email": "peter_jones@gmail.com", "last_name": "Jones", "first_name": "Peter"}
]}


Estructura de datos XML:
<data>
    <datum>
        <firstName>John</firstName> <lastName>Doe</lastName>
    </datum>
    <datum>
        <firstName>Anna</firstName> <lastName>Smith</lastName>
    </datum>
    <datum>
        <firstName>Peter</firstName> <lastName>Jones</lastName>
    </datum>
</data>

